      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>Two fragments from a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">door post</rs> from the right side of a door, 1. fragment with right side surviving (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.15</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.19</measure> x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.07</measure>). 2. larger fragment ( <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">1.34</measure> ×  <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.42</measure> × <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.42</measure>) broken above and below and damaged on the surface.</p>
</div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        
      <p>i a: <rs type="execution" key="scalpro">inscribed</rs> on a projecting area of 1; b (inscribed area <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.26</measure>, H. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.30</measure>) is inscribed on 2, and  ii. is inscribed some <measure value="0.1" type="length" dim="none">10 cm</measure> lower down.</p>
</div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>i. a: ll.1, 3-5, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.015</measure>; l.2, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.01</measure>; dots on either side of Α in l.1, and Ε in l.2, between S and E in l.3. b: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.008</measure>; dots for stops in ll 7, 10. Ligatures: ΗΝ ll 9, 10, ΗΝ ll. 11, 12. ii. Lightly cut and sprawling, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03-0.05</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div n="date" type="description">
        <head>Date</head><p>i. <date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0200" exact="none">Second century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>); ii. <date notAfter="0600" notBefore="0400">Fifth to sixth centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">location</rs>, <rs type="criteria">content</rs>)</p>
      </div>

